// Message
// 
// Messages alert a user to information they must immediately consider before proceeding on to the normal content of the page.
//
// .hidden - Text Blocks can be hidden
// .visible - Text Blocks can be set to visible if they need to force themselves to be shown.
// .floating - A message can float above content that it is related to
// .compact - A message can only take up the width of its content.
// .red - A message can be formatted to be red
// .blue - A message can be formatted to be blue
// .yellow - A message can be formatted to be yellow
// .green - A message can be formatted to be green
// .small - A message can have small size
// .large - A message can have large size
// .huge - A message can have huge size
// .massive - A message can have massive size
//
// Markup:
// <div class="ui {$modifiers} message">
//   <div class="header">
//     Welcome back!
//   </div>
//   <p>
//     It's good to see you again. I have had a lot to think about since our last visit, I've changed much as a person and I can see that you have too.
//   </p>
//   <p>
//     Perhaps we can talk about it if you have the time.
//   </p>
// </div>
//
// Styleguide 3.8

